<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='669990' id='t-669990'>Years later, she moved to America.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='671603' id='t-671603'>She had a baby,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='672447' id='t-672447'>One day she looked, and on the floor,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='674203' id='t-674203'>her infant son had picked up her bra,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='677274' id='t-677274'>and had her bra on his face.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='679133' id='t-679133'>And that's where the idea came from.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='680814' id='t-680814'>She came to the Ig Nobel ceremony</span>
