<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='748574' id='t-748574'>[&quot;Wolfgang Ketterle, Nobel 
laureate (2001) in physics&quot;]</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='763663' id='t-763663'>I myself own an emergency bra. (Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='767283' id='t-767283'>It's my favorite bra,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='769621' id='t-769621'>but I would be happy to 
share it with any of you,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='772273' id='t-772273'>should the need arise.</span>
